WEBVTT

00:00:45.086 --> 00:00:46.880
-It's just a bandage replacement.
-No, Bok.

00:00:46.963 --> 00:00:48.006
It's a no, okay?

00:00:48.089 --> 00:00:49.966
Dara, bring her back to the hospital.

00:00:50.049 --> 00:00:51.217
You don't get to tell me what to do.

00:00:51.301 --> 00:00:54.054
And I won't lose the person I love again.

00:00:57.474 --> 00:00:58.808
You're wrong about me.

00:00:58.892 --> 00:01:01.436
I am the same Mikoy you know.

00:01:12.197 --> 00:01:13.114
Goodbye,

00:01:13.615 --> 00:01:19.287
Mr. Michael "Mikoy" D. Pinagpala!

00:02:12.382 --> 00:02:13.883
Looks like they came through here.

00:02:14.926 --> 00:02:16.719
Copy, Agent Sianong.

00:02:32.277 --> 00:02:33.444
Now what?

00:02:36.197 --> 00:02:37.657
Can we talk now?

00:03:19.032 --> 00:03:20.950
Call EMS. Call EMS now.

00:03:23.703 --> 00:03:24.662
Hello?

00:03:53.858 --> 00:03:55.026
What?

00:03:55.109 --> 00:03:56.319
Why are you staring at me?

00:03:56.986 --> 00:03:57.820
Why?

00:03:57.904 --> 00:03:59.989
Are you judging me? You're judging me?

00:04:01.741 --> 00:04:04.035
Are you going to say I'm greedy?
That I'm fat?

00:04:05.536 --> 00:04:07.372
Well, I deserve this, okay?

00:04:07.455 --> 00:04:09.165
I deserve to stress-eat.

00:04:09.249 --> 00:04:12.043
Because of all the stress
you've brought into my life.

00:04:36.609 --> 00:04:38.695
And I need this.

00:04:38.778 --> 00:04:42.115
I need this
because you're a lying bastard!

00:04:42.782 --> 00:04:44.075
Wait a second.

00:04:44.742 --> 00:04:47.745
Am I the only one
who lied in this relationship?

00:04:47.829 --> 00:04:49.414
Am I the only one

00:04:49.497 --> 00:04:51.207
who kept secrets between us?

00:04:51.791 --> 00:04:52.750
You did too!

00:04:52.834 --> 00:04:54.627
You've been hiding a lot too!

00:04:55.253 --> 00:04:58.881
So I, deserve to stress-eat too.

00:04:59.590 --> 00:05:00.508
This!

00:05:11.644 --> 00:05:12.729
Got it.

00:05:24.574 --> 00:05:25.783
You know what?

00:05:26.367 --> 00:05:27.744
You've been so mean to me.

00:05:27.827 --> 00:05:29.287
Seriously, you're awful!

00:05:29.370 --> 00:05:31.414
You almost got me killed tonight.

00:05:35.126 --> 00:05:36.461
Why me?

00:05:37.170 --> 00:05:38.921
You're the government snitch between us.

00:05:40.089 --> 00:05:41.299
Snitch?

00:05:42.467 --> 00:05:44.552
It's called being a police asset.

00:05:45.178 --> 00:05:46.554
What's wrong with you?

00:05:46.637 --> 00:05:48.514
That's the same thing, idiot!

00:05:48.598 --> 00:05:51.225
"Idiot"? At least I'm not a killer.

00:05:51.309 --> 00:05:52.310
Okay?

00:05:52.894 --> 00:05:54.395
Just shut up and eat.

00:05:56.230 --> 00:05:57.607
What am I doing?

00:07:03.881 --> 00:07:04.924
You know?

00:07:05.508 --> 00:07:09.387
In all fairness, we managed
to find a hidden gem.

00:07:10.304 --> 00:07:15.768
Or maybe food just tastes better
after surviving death.

00:07:21.399 --> 00:07:22.525
Sorry.

00:07:25.278 --> 00:07:26.237
Okay.

00:07:28.573 --> 00:07:29.615
Now…

00:07:32.869 --> 00:07:34.412
that we've eaten,

00:07:36.164 --> 00:07:38.791
how about you start telling me everything?

00:07:40.585 --> 00:07:41.836
Now.

00:07:41.919 --> 00:07:43.337
No secrets.

00:07:44.672 --> 00:07:46.424
No more lies.

00:07:46.507 --> 00:07:47.800
Can you do that?

00:07:55.933 --> 00:07:56.767
Okay.

00:07:57.518 --> 00:07:58.519
Let's start.

00:07:59.770 --> 00:08:01.063
From the beginning.

00:08:05.443 --> 00:08:06.319
Okay.

00:08:07.069 --> 00:08:09.071
You really want to know everything?

00:08:10.406 --> 00:08:11.324
Fine.

00:08:12.909 --> 00:08:15.786
Let's start from the very beginning.

00:08:16.412 --> 00:08:19.415
Where it all truly began.

00:08:25.838 --> 00:08:28.132
Go on. Let's push it.

00:08:28.216 --> 00:08:30.510
Take a deep breath. Then push it.

00:08:34.972 --> 00:08:35.890
Ouch!

00:08:35.973 --> 00:08:36.849
What?

00:08:36.933 --> 00:08:38.309
-Are you messing with me?
-What?

00:08:38.392 --> 00:08:39.393
No!

00:08:39.477 --> 00:08:41.896
-Do you think this is a joke?
-Ouch!

00:08:41.979 --> 00:08:43.981
Come on. It was just a joke!

00:08:44.065 --> 00:08:46.067
You can't take a joke. I was only kidding.

00:08:46.150 --> 00:08:48.611
And in this situation,
you're still making jokes?

00:08:49.695 --> 00:08:51.239
Sorry!

00:08:51.322 --> 00:08:53.241
When I said

00:08:53.324 --> 00:08:54.700
start from the beginning,

00:08:54.784 --> 00:08:58.538
I didn't mean start from the beginning
since the day you were born!

00:08:58.621 --> 00:09:00.206
Okay.

00:09:00.289 --> 00:09:01.541
It was just a joke.

00:09:06.754 --> 00:09:08.089
That hurts.

00:09:20.518 --> 00:09:22.395
That's Mikoy and Chiara. Let's get them.

00:09:22.979 --> 00:09:24.063
No, let's go.

00:09:40.871 --> 00:09:42.957
Come on. You're acting
like it hurts that much.

00:09:43.541 --> 00:09:44.875
Are you a rookie?

00:09:45.376 --> 00:09:48.212
It's not like you didn't take
all those punches from me earlier.

00:09:48.796 --> 00:09:49.964
It's just that this is the first time

00:09:50.047 --> 00:09:52.300
I've reacted to all the punches
and kicks you gave me earlier.

00:09:53.050 --> 00:09:54.260
You're unbelievable!

00:09:54.343 --> 00:09:57.305
You turned me into half boyfriend,
half punching bag.

00:10:01.434 --> 00:10:02.977
That hurts!

00:10:12.236 --> 00:10:13.821
Why are you looking at me like that?

00:10:28.711 --> 00:10:29.795
What are we going to do?

00:10:31.005 --> 00:10:33.841
As I've said, let's go.
Let's just let them be.

00:10:36.594 --> 00:10:38.304
Agent Dara, do you trust me?

00:10:38.804 --> 00:10:40.014
Ma'am…

00:10:40.097 --> 00:10:41.807
Then trust me on this.

00:10:42.350 --> 00:10:44.894
We'll leave them alone.
We'll leave them tonight.

00:10:45.770 --> 00:10:47.897
And don't you dare report this to anyone.

00:10:47.980 --> 00:10:49.315
Not even to Sianong.

00:10:49.398 --> 00:10:50.566
That's my order.

00:10:50.650 --> 00:10:51.817
Is that clear?

00:10:52.318 --> 00:10:53.778
Loud and clear, ma'am.

00:10:54.403 --> 00:10:55.446
Now, go.

00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:06.123
Are you staring at my face because

00:11:06.207 --> 00:11:07.917
you are trying to figure out
where you'll punch me next?

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:09.001
Is that it?

00:11:10.294 --> 00:11:11.712
No.

00:11:12.546 --> 00:11:13.547
No.

00:11:14.632 --> 00:11:16.592
You just look cute when you eat.

00:11:17.510 --> 00:11:20.471
You leave so much food behind,
like a little kid.

00:11:21.889 --> 00:11:23.724
I really do look cute when I eat.

00:11:23.808 --> 00:11:25.768
People say I'm like a baby.

00:11:43.452 --> 00:11:44.328
Wow!

00:11:44.954 --> 00:11:46.163
How sweet of you.

00:11:46.872 --> 00:11:50.584
Wiping something off my lips
and everything.

00:12:08.727 --> 00:12:10.396
When just a while ago,

00:12:10.479 --> 00:12:12.815
you looked like you wanted
to fill my body with bullets.

00:12:12.898 --> 00:12:14.066
You know,

00:12:14.150 --> 00:12:16.110
your mood swings are pretty intense.

00:12:16.819 --> 00:12:18.362
Literally deadly.

00:12:18.988 --> 00:12:21.323
For your information,
this isn't a mood swing.

00:12:21.407 --> 00:12:23.492
I'm not hormonal right now.

00:12:25.619 --> 00:12:27.204
Do you really think

00:12:27.746 --> 00:12:30.040
if I intended to kill you,

00:12:30.541 --> 00:12:31.876
you'd still be alive?

00:12:31.959 --> 00:12:35.004
You'd still be sitting there
pouting at me like that?

00:12:37.339 --> 00:12:38.966
Just get his statement.

00:12:39.049 --> 00:12:39.925
Okay.

00:12:40.759 --> 00:12:44.180
Send EMS over here.
There are still injured people here, okay?

00:12:47.516 --> 00:12:50.144
What time did all of this start exactly?

00:12:53.147 --> 00:12:57.359
How many people did you see come here?

00:12:59.904 --> 00:13:01.113
Hello, Agent Sianong?

00:13:01.197 --> 00:13:02.781
Hello, Dara. How are you?

00:13:02.865 --> 00:13:03.908
Have you arrived at the hospital yet?

00:13:03.991 --> 00:13:07.328
We're five minutes away.
We're almost there.

00:13:07.411 --> 00:13:09.955
How's Alex doing?

00:13:10.706 --> 00:13:12.249
Agent Alex is asleep.

00:13:12.333 --> 00:13:16.003
I told her to get some rest
while we're on the way.

00:13:16.086 --> 00:13:17.213
Okay, okay.

00:13:17.296 --> 00:13:18.255
That's good.

00:13:19.256 --> 00:13:20.883
How are things there?

00:13:20.966 --> 00:13:24.053
Well, we've found the place

00:13:24.136 --> 00:13:27.473
where it looks like Mikoy
and La Fornarina fought.

00:13:32.144 --> 00:13:34.772
Looks like the fight
between the two was intense.

00:13:35.356 --> 00:13:39.610
But we're still gathering information
and securing the area, also the evidence.

00:13:39.693 --> 00:13:42.530
But unfortunately,

00:13:42.613 --> 00:13:46.075
we haven't found
any trace of where Mikoy is.

00:13:46.742 --> 00:13:48.410
Or even Chiara.

00:13:48.494 --> 00:13:50.454
Are you still looking for them, sir?

00:13:50.538 --> 00:13:52.081
Yes.

00:13:52.164 --> 00:13:55.960
I've already sent out a sweeper team
just to spread out further

00:13:56.043 --> 00:14:00.923
and see if they can find
any more traces of Chiara and Mikoy.

00:14:01.966 --> 00:14:05.386
But the real reason I called
was just to check on you.

00:14:05.469 --> 00:14:07.930
I will give you
a briefing tomorrow, I promise.

00:14:08.013 --> 00:14:09.223
But for now,

00:14:09.807 --> 00:14:12.351
please just make sure Alex will be okay.

00:14:32.454 --> 00:14:34.206
I'm really angry at you,

00:14:34.290 --> 00:14:35.124
yes.

00:14:37.376 --> 00:14:40.629
But do you really think I'd just kill you

00:14:40.713 --> 00:14:42.798
without hearing your side?

00:14:42.882 --> 00:14:45.009
Do you think I'm that shallow?

00:14:45.759 --> 00:14:47.678
No matter what you say,

00:14:48.846 --> 00:14:53.726
you can't change the fact
that you cheated on me

00:14:54.685 --> 00:14:56.604
and lied to me.

00:14:58.606 --> 00:15:01.358
So now I'm going to let you
explain yourself.

00:15:01.984 --> 00:15:06.697
And after your explanation,
I'll decide whether I'll kill you or not.

00:15:07.448 --> 00:15:09.158
That's a lot of pressure.

00:15:09.241 --> 00:15:11.660
What is this? An impromptu thesis defense?

00:15:12.661 --> 00:15:15.205
I don't even give chances to others.

00:15:16.457 --> 00:15:18.292
This is your only chance.

00:15:29.511 --> 00:15:30.429
Okay.

00:15:32.306 --> 00:15:33.724
Okay, listen.

00:15:34.475 --> 00:15:35.351
Okay?

00:15:37.436 --> 00:15:39.605
What? You're taking forever!

00:15:39.688 --> 00:15:40.898
All right, here it goes!

00:15:41.523 --> 00:15:43.067
No hurting.

00:15:43.150 --> 00:15:44.151
Promise?

00:15:46.070 --> 00:15:47.488
No hurting.

00:15:50.199 --> 00:15:51.116
Okay.

00:15:53.744 --> 00:15:55.037
So here's the thing.

00:15:55.663 --> 00:15:57.081
You know what?

00:15:58.582 --> 00:16:00.960
Just ask me whatever you want to know,

00:16:01.043 --> 00:16:03.253
so that way, I'll know
exactly what to answer.

00:16:03.337 --> 00:16:04.338
Sounds good?

00:16:08.258 --> 00:16:09.093
Okay.

00:16:10.010 --> 00:16:12.304
So when I first met you in Prague,

00:16:12.388 --> 00:16:14.473
were you already a police asset then?

00:16:14.556 --> 00:16:16.058
Had you already trained?

00:16:16.141 --> 00:16:18.727
What about your charm?
Did you train that too?

00:16:18.811 --> 00:16:20.479
So I'd kiss you right away?

00:16:21.063 --> 00:16:22.439
Of course not!

00:16:22.523 --> 00:16:23.857
What do I look like to you?

00:16:23.941 --> 00:16:25.693
Do I look like a cop?

00:16:25.776 --> 00:16:27.403
Or some action star?

00:16:27.486 --> 00:16:29.446
Well, after those moves
you pulled on me earlier,

00:16:29.530 --> 00:16:31.740
yes, you kind of do
look like an action star.

00:16:31.824 --> 00:16:33.325
Whatever!

00:16:33.409 --> 00:16:35.119
I just happened to run into you there.

00:16:35.744 --> 00:16:37.705
Everything about when we first met, okay,

00:16:37.788 --> 00:16:39.456
all of it was real.

00:16:39.540 --> 00:16:40.791
That was all me.

00:16:40.874 --> 00:16:42.668
I wasn't a police asset yet.

00:16:43.711 --> 00:16:45.587
You didn't know me before that?

00:16:48.507 --> 00:16:49.550
No.

00:16:52.344 --> 00:16:56.140
So… are you saying

00:16:57.933 --> 00:17:00.352
we're just two perfect strangers

00:17:00.436 --> 00:17:04.148
who met and fell in love with each other?

00:17:07.818 --> 00:17:08.694
Exactly.

00:17:08.777 --> 00:17:10.404
When I met you,

00:17:11.280 --> 00:17:13.115
I felt so at ease.

00:17:14.283 --> 00:17:15.451
You know what I thought?

00:17:16.076 --> 00:17:18.829
What good thing
could I have done in my life

00:17:18.912 --> 00:17:21.790
to meet a woman
who, besides being beautiful,

00:17:22.416 --> 00:17:24.710
has a generous heart like yours?

00:17:27.963 --> 00:17:29.381
But of course,

00:17:29.923 --> 00:17:33.177
you're not a cough
for me to be an expectorant.

00:17:33.719 --> 00:17:35.554
So I didn't get my hopes up.

00:17:35.637 --> 00:17:37.681
I was just a lowly waiter back then.

00:17:38.307 --> 00:17:40.267
And I wasn't even from Prague.

00:17:40.350 --> 00:17:41.560
I honestly thought

00:17:41.643 --> 00:17:44.855
that would be the first
and last time I'd ever see you.

00:17:46.315 --> 00:17:47.316
But…

00:17:48.442 --> 00:17:49.443
But?

00:17:50.360 --> 00:17:53.238
You're like a rare Pokémon.

00:17:53.322 --> 00:17:55.115
You just suddenly appear

00:17:55.199 --> 00:17:58.035
when I'm not ready for it.

00:17:59.036 --> 00:18:01.497
And then you even kissed me.

00:18:14.510 --> 00:18:15.385
Wow!

00:18:16.762 --> 00:18:18.263
You kissed me too!

00:18:18.972 --> 00:18:20.933
Of course that's how I felt back then.

00:18:21.016 --> 00:18:23.393
Like you needed someone with you.

00:18:23.977 --> 00:18:27.523
And of course, the kiss
was a nice bonus, right?

00:18:30.234 --> 00:18:31.819
Well, you're not wrong.

00:18:36.281 --> 00:18:38.534
How was I supposed to know
you like to kiss?

00:18:38.617 --> 00:18:39.743
Come on.

00:18:41.495 --> 00:18:42.871
Any follow-up questions?

00:18:43.455 --> 00:18:44.540
It's true, though.

00:18:50.170 --> 00:18:53.966
Because my Czech crew
was ambushed by a Russian mob.

00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:55.509
Wait a minute.

00:18:56.093 --> 00:18:59.555
So that means…
you had just come from a fight?

00:18:59.638 --> 00:19:00.931
No.

00:19:01.014 --> 00:19:04.268
After we visited the zoo, was when I…

00:19:05.269 --> 00:19:06.520
Wait a minute.

00:19:06.603 --> 00:19:07.813
That means…

00:19:08.689 --> 00:19:12.442
our kiss gave you an energy boost

00:19:12.526 --> 00:19:15.362
to fight off those Russian mobsters?

00:19:15.946 --> 00:19:17.072
I knew it!

00:19:17.156 --> 00:19:19.449
You flatter yourself too much!

00:19:19.533 --> 00:19:21.243
You're unbelievable.

00:19:23.287 --> 00:19:24.496
You know?

00:19:26.165 --> 00:19:27.624
You're a good kisser.

00:19:27.708 --> 00:19:29.376
-Just?
-But!

00:19:29.459 --> 00:19:32.045
You're only around top-five-ish.

00:19:32.129 --> 00:19:33.130
Wow!

00:19:34.047 --> 00:19:36.925
Just top-five-ish only?

00:19:38.343 --> 00:19:39.178
Is that so?

00:19:39.845 --> 00:19:41.847
Well, top five is fine.

00:19:41.930 --> 00:19:44.224
At least there's room
for improvement, right?

00:19:45.726 --> 00:19:48.979
All I know is I won't stop
until I'm number one on your list.

00:19:49.605 --> 00:19:51.565
You're so full of yourself!

00:19:54.651 --> 00:19:57.446
When were you recruited by GAGO?

00:19:59.406 --> 00:20:01.200
Okay, here we go.

00:20:02.075 --> 00:20:03.827
It started

00:20:04.995 --> 00:20:08.790
the day after your bald father
had me kidnapped.

00:20:10.250 --> 00:20:11.501
Man, you go with us.

00:20:11.585 --> 00:20:13.754
Sir, wait, please.

00:20:13.837 --> 00:20:15.631
And then,

00:20:15.714 --> 00:20:18.717
the day after we officially
became a couple,

00:20:18.800 --> 00:20:21.595
that was when I first met
Agent Alex and Agent Sianong.

00:20:24.598 --> 00:20:27.643
-I'm sorry.
-I'm Special Agent Alexandria Cortez.

00:20:27.726 --> 00:20:29.770
And I'm afraid
you'll have to come with me,

00:20:29.853 --> 00:20:31.897
Mr. Mikoy D. Pinagpala.

00:20:35.359 --> 00:20:38.612
Remember when I told you
my brother got arrested?

00:20:40.030 --> 00:20:40.906
That was because of them.

00:20:42.115 --> 00:20:43.075
They set him up,

00:20:43.158 --> 00:20:45.535
so I'd be forced to accept their mission.

00:20:46.370 --> 00:20:48.330
So they forced you?

00:20:50.249 --> 00:20:51.333
At first.

00:20:52.251 --> 00:20:53.543
But of course,

00:20:54.294 --> 00:20:58.173
there came a point
where I convinced myself that…

00:20:59.091 --> 00:21:01.218
this was the right thing to do.

00:21:03.095 --> 00:21:06.723
Actually, Chiara, even now,
I still keep convincing myself that…

00:21:08.809 --> 00:21:10.978
as long as I work for the agency,

00:21:11.561 --> 00:21:13.647
I can protect you from your family.

00:21:15.482 --> 00:21:18.277
In this world of yours.

00:21:20.904 --> 00:21:22.948
That's why I've been doing all this.

00:21:27.244 --> 00:21:28.328
But you know,

00:21:29.621 --> 00:21:32.332
it feels like this mission
is consuming me.

00:21:33.792 --> 00:21:36.503
Every day, my heart grows
heavier and heavier.

00:21:38.714 --> 00:21:40.215
Because I know

00:21:41.258 --> 00:21:43.760
I haven't been honest
with the person I love.

00:21:48.432 --> 00:21:51.393
Because I wasn't honest with you either.

00:21:56.857 --> 00:21:58.025
Mikoy.

00:22:02.237 --> 00:22:06.033
I just didn't want you
to see this side of me.

00:22:11.413 --> 00:22:13.999
I was terrified that you'd find out.

00:22:19.212 --> 00:22:22.132
Because this side of me
isn't easy to love.

00:22:38.607 --> 00:22:40.650
Chiara, don't ever say that.

00:22:41.818 --> 00:22:42.778
Okay?

00:22:46.114 --> 00:22:47.783
We all deserve to love.

00:22:48.909 --> 00:22:50.368
Especially you.

00:22:53.497 --> 00:22:54.414
Mikoy.

00:22:56.416 --> 00:22:58.168
Stop making a fool of me.

00:22:59.753 --> 00:23:00.670
Chiara.

00:23:01.755 --> 00:23:03.965
You're not the fool here, okay?

00:23:06.384 --> 00:23:08.345
Hey. I am.

00:23:11.264 --> 00:23:13.934
Because despite everything
I've learned about you,

00:23:16.561 --> 00:23:18.814
Chiara, my feelings for you
haven't changed at all.

00:23:20.482 --> 00:23:22.192
If that's what you call foolish,

00:23:23.652 --> 00:23:24.736
then yes,

00:23:25.403 --> 00:23:28.156
I must be the biggest fool in the world.

00:23:29.324 --> 00:23:30.617
And I'll accept that.

00:23:38.500 --> 00:23:41.211
How long have you known
everything about me?

00:23:43.380 --> 00:23:44.506
Just yesterday.

00:23:46.591 --> 00:23:47.467
Just kidding.

00:23:55.767 --> 00:23:57.227
I've felt it for a long time.

00:24:12.409 --> 00:24:13.827
I've been suspicious for a while.

00:24:15.620 --> 00:24:17.164
But I ignored it.

00:24:18.665 --> 00:24:22.419
Actually, even back then,
I never really cared who you were.

00:24:23.879 --> 00:24:25.922
Chiara, I don't care about your past,

00:24:26.882 --> 00:24:28.425
your present, or your future.

00:24:29.759 --> 00:24:32.012
Because the truth is,
there's only one thing I want.

00:24:35.140 --> 00:24:37.142
I just want to be with you.

00:24:49.779 --> 00:24:50.947
Chiara, I'm sorry.

00:25:05.086 --> 00:25:06.504
No kissing allowed here.

00:25:06.588 --> 00:25:08.006
Can't you read?

00:25:09.090 --> 00:25:10.300
Really?

00:25:12.052 --> 00:25:13.011
Here.

00:25:22.062 --> 00:25:23.355
Well,

00:25:23.438 --> 00:25:25.232
Mr. Pinagpala.

00:25:28.360 --> 00:25:31.613
There's one more thing
you don't know about me.

00:25:37.369 --> 00:25:38.578
What's that?

00:25:38.662 --> 00:25:41.248
The thing about me is…

00:25:43.458 --> 00:25:45.168
I don't really care

00:25:45.877 --> 00:25:47.671
whether it's forbidden or wrong,

00:25:48.922 --> 00:25:50.715
because all I know is,

00:25:53.843 --> 00:25:55.804
I love you so much.

00:26:18.368 --> 00:26:19.661
Is there anything we can do for you?

00:27:21.222 --> 00:27:22.640
Wait, time out!